{"id":199,"parent_id":196,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":199,"title":"1 Thessalonians 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Thes.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","The Saints are told to perfect that which is lacking in their faith."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.1","order":"03.15.003.21532"},["b","1"],"Wherefore when we could no longer forbear, we thought it good to be left at",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Athens"],"alone;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.2","order":"03.15.003.21533"},["b","2"],"And sent",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Timotheus"],", our brother, and minister of God, and our fellowlabourer in the gospel of Christ, to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"establish"],"you, and to comfort you concerning your faith:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.3","order":"03.15.003.21534"},["b","3"],"That no man should be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"moved"],"by these",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"afflictions"],": for yourselves know that we are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"appointed"],"thereunto."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.4","order":"03.15.003.21535"},["b","4"],"For verily, when we were with you, we told you before that we should suffer tribulation; even as it came to pass, and ye know."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.5","order":"03.15.003.21536"},["b","5"],"For this cause, when I could no longer forbear, I sent to know your faith, lest by some means the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"tempter"],"have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"tempted"],"you, and our labour be in vain."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.6","order":"03.15.003.21537"},["b","6"],"But now when Timotheus came from you unto us, and brought us good tidings of your faith and charity, and that ye have good remembrance of us always, desiring greatly to see us, as we also",["i","to see"],"you:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.7","order":"03.15.003.21538"},["b","7"],"Therefore, brethren, we were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"comforted"],"over you in all our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"affliction"],"and distress by your faith:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.8","order":"03.15.003.21539"},["b","8"],"For now we live, if ye stand fast in the Lord."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.9","order":"03.15.003.21540"},["b","9"],"For what thanks can we render to God again for you, for all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"joy"],"wherewith we joy for your sakes before our God;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.10","order":"03.15.003.21541"},["b","10"],"Night and day praying exceedingly that we might see your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"face"],", and might",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"perfect"],"that which is lacking in your faith?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.11","order":"03.15.003.21542"},["b","11"],"Now God himself and our Father, and our Lord Jesus Christ, direct our way unto you."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.12","order":"03.15.003.21543"},["b","12"],"And the Lord make you to increase and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"abound"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"love"],"one toward another, and toward all",["i","men,"],"even as we",["i","do"],"toward you:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.13","order":"03.15.003.21544"},["b","13"],"To the end he may stablish your hearts unblameable in holiness before God, even our Father, at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"coming"],"of our Lord Jesus Christ with all his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"saints"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.1a","order":"03.15.003.21545"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.15"},"Acts 17:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.2a","order":"03.15.003.21547"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.1.1-2"},"Acts 16:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.10.10-11"},"1 Cor. 16:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19"},"2 Cor. 1:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.1"},"1 Thes. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.2b","order":"03.15.003.21549"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.25"},"Rom. 16:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.3a","order":"03.15.003.21551"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"disturbed, perturbed."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.3b","order":"03.15.003.21553"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.23"},"Acts 20:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.24.23-24"},"JS—H 1:24 (23–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.3c","order":"03.15.003.21555"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.15.15-16"},"Acts 9:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.5a","order":"03.15.003.21557"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.39.39-40,47"},"D&C 29:39 (39–40, 47)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.4.3-4"},"Moses 4:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.5b","order":"03.15.003.21559"},["b","5b"],["span.small","GR"],"put to trial, test."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.7a","order":"03.15.003.21561"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sustaining-church-leaders"},"TG Sustaining Church Leaders"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.7b","order":"03.15.003.21563"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.9a","order":"03.15.003.21565"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.11.11-13"},"Alma 26:11 (11–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.16.14-16"},"D&C 18:16 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.10a","order":"03.15.003.21567"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.17"},"1 Thes. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.10b","order":"03.15.003.21569"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.12a","order":"03.15.003.21571"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1"},"1 Thes. 4:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.12b","order":"03.15.003.21573"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.45"},"D&C 121:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.13a","order":"03.15.003.21575"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.7.7-8"},"1 Cor. 1:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.19"},"1 Thes. 2:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.7"},"Rev. 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.12"},"22:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.13b","order":"03.15.003.21577"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/saints"},"TG Saints"],"."]]}
